|YKOOn Darkwind, we give players the option to newbify their characters should they
choose to do so. This entails 'killing' them down to level 1, reducing all
stats down to 1, and resetting a couple other things the character has learned
throughout their life. It's merely a quick way for you to start somewhat over,
but not quite from scratch.

You will need to find someone to help you accomplish this dasterdly deed though.
If you ask around you can probably find such a person willing to help you
'see the light' a little early.

|WKBNOTE: Attempting to newbify yourself by repeatedly killing yourself off is
against the spirit of the game and is punishable by the Gods of Darkwind.


